name: Birds Eye Chips And Tasty Chicken Schnitzel Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 pkt 900g Frozen Birds Eye Golden Crunch Chips  Straight Cut
1 jar 475g chicken tonight creamy mushroom sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Cook frozen Birds Eye Chips and preprepared chicken schnitzels following packet directions.
Warm Chicken Tonight Sauce in saucepan or in a microwave safe container.
Serve schnitzels with Birds Eye Chips and garden salad. Pour over Chicken Tonight Sauce and serve immediately.
